OL,6, Over the years there have been legends.
OL,7, From the BBC you had the likes of David
OL,8, Allan, David Miles, Peter Bolgar, Peter
OL,9, Brook, Michael Maine, to name a few who
OL,10, were there to introduce the programmes 
OL,11, to you on either BBC1 or BBC2.         
OL,13, They were never in-vision so it did    
OL,14, feel like the globe or the clock was   
OL,15, talking to you. With the BBC it had a  
OL,16, good strong list of announcers over the
OL,17, regions. Until 1980 the regions had in-
OL,18, vision announcing but only at certain  
OL,19, times. With the South East, they were  
OL,20, very seldom in-vision... very rare     
OL,21, in fact.                               
