OL,6, Although they were usually out of      
OL,7, vision some announcers doubled up as   
OL,8, news readers which in turn made them   
OL,9, more recognisable. I loved the voices  
OL,10, of this time from the 1960s to the     
OL,11, 1990s, something sadly that is slightly
OL,12, lacking with today's announcers.       
OL,14, For ITV you had legendary announcers   
OL,15, like Redvers Kyle, Colin Weston, Steve 
OL,16, Hamilton, Tony Currie, Neville Wainless
OL,17, etc... whose voices graced our ITV     
OL,18, screens over the years in the different
OL,19, regions. With the exception of YTV most
OL,20, of the ITV regions were in-vision so   
OL,21, announcers became well-known stars.    
