OL,6, Even though Redvers was in-vision on   
OL,7, Rediffusion London he very rarely      
OL,8, appeared in-vision on Yorkshire        
OL,9, Television but his voice was always    
OL,10, recognised very quickly.               
OL,12, For me I was born in the late 1980s    
OL,13, which meant I grew up remembering the  
OL,14, voices of the 1990s. With Ulster       
OL,15, Television (now UTV) we had the        
OL,16, legendary Julian Simmons who'd light   
OL,17, up anyone's day with his fantastic     
OL,18, announcing and intro's, especially into
OL,19, Coronation Street.                     
