OL,6, After looking back on clips of         
OL,7, continuity announcers over the years it
OL,8, was always a nice feeling of warmth    
OL,9, that radiated off them, especially when
OL,10, it came to closedowns.                 
OL,12, When it came to Christmas closedowns   
OL,13, there have been stories of announcers  
OL,14, being rather tipsy, which would've made
OL,15, it even more fun, as you wouldn't know 
OL,16, what they would end up saying!         
OL,18, And at New Year some of them would've  
OL,19, been celebrating to compensate being at
OL,20, work with I'd say a right glass of     
OL,21, champagne and a few party streamers.   
